001package org.consensusj.bitcoin.json.pojo;
002
003import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;
004import org.bitcoinj.base.Coin;
005import org.bitcoinj.base.Sha256Hash;
006
007/**
008 * Result of `gettxoutsetinfo`
009 */
010public class TxOutSetInfo {
011    private final int height;
012    private final Sha256Hash bestBlock;
013    private final long transactions;
014    private final long txOuts;
015    private final long bogoSize;
016    private final Sha256Hash hashSerialized2;
017    private final long diskSize;
018    private final Coin totalAmount;
019
020
021    public TxOutSetInfo(@JsonProperty("height")             int         height,
022                        @JsonProperty("bestblock")          Sha256Hash  bestBlock,
023                        @JsonProperty("transactions")       long        transactions,
024                        @JsonProperty("txouts")             long        txOuts,
025                        @JsonProperty("bogosize")           long        bogoSize,
026                        @JsonProperty("hash_serialized_2")  Sha256Hash  hashSerialized2,
027                        @JsonProperty("disk_size")          long        diskSize,
028                        @JsonProperty("total_amount")       Coin        totalAmount) {
029        this.height = height;
030        this.bestBlock = bestBlock;
031        this.transactions = transactions;
032        this.txOuts = txOuts;
033        this.bogoSize = bogoSize;
034        this.hashSerialized2 = hashSerialized2;
035        this.diskSize = diskSize;
036        this.totalAmount = totalAmount;
037    }
038
039    public int getHeight() {
040        return height;
041    }
042
043    public Sha256Hash getBestBlock() {
044        return bestBlock;
045    }
046
047    public long getTransactions() {
048        return transactions;
049    }
050
051    public long getTxOuts() {
052        return txOuts;
053    }
054
055    public long getBogoSize() {
056        return bogoSize;
057    }
058
059    public Sha256Hash getHashSerialized2() {
060        return hashSerialized2;
061    }
062
063    public long getDiskSize() {
064        return diskSize;
065    }
066
067    public Coin getTotalAmount() {
068        return totalAmount;
069    }
070}
